<section id="candidate">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sect-head">
        <div class="eyebrow">Are You a Candidate?</div>
        <h2 class="display" style="margin-top: 14px">
          Revive Veneers work for most people. They're not right for everyone.
        </h2>
        <p class="sub">
          They're designed for people with healthy teeth who want a
          better-looking smile, not for people who need dental treatment.
          Here's an honest breakdown of who they're built for.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cand-grid">
        <div class="ccard ideal">
          <div class="ctitle"><span class="cdot"></span>Ideal candidates</div>
          <ul>
            <li>Generally healthy teeth and gums</li>
            <li>
              Want to improve the appearance of stained, slightly gapped, or
              worn teeth
            </li>
            <li>All upper or all lower teeth present</li>
            <li>No active gum disease or recent major dental work</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ccard good">
          <div class="ctitle">
            <span class="cdot"></span>Good candidates, extended timeline
          </div>
          <ul>
            <li>Small to medium gaps in teeth</li>
            <li>Minor bite issues (slight overbite or underbite)</li>
            <li>Worn or short teeth from grinding</li>
            <li>One or two missing teeth not at the end of the arch</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ccard consult">
          <div class="ctitle">
            <span class="cdot"></span>Consult before ordering
          </div>
          <ul>
            <li>Active gum disease or significant gum recession</li>
            <li>Severe crossbite or bite alignment issues</li>
            <li>Recent major dental work within the last 3 months</li>
            <li>Multiple missing teeth or teeth missing at end of arch</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ccard not">
          <div class="ctitle"><span class="cdot"></span>Not a candidate</div>
          <ul>
            <li>No remaining teeth in the arch you want covered</li>
            <li>Currently wearing full dentures</li>
            <li>Active oral infection or untreated periodontal disease</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
